{"ID":"20230723224532-4ltekxk","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20230723224532-4ltekxk","title":"2.1.4 计算机网络协议","updated":"20230723224622"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230723224548-5o26kzk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723224548-5o26kzk","updated":"20230723224548"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"越接近硬件的层次为底层 layer1，越接近应用程序的则是高层 layer7，"}]},{"ID":"20230723224548-jfpayav","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723224548-jfpayav","updated":"20230723224548"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不论接收端还是发射端，每一层次只认识对方的同一层次的数据"}]},{"ID":"20230723224548-ce9zncx","Type":"NodeTable","TableAligns":[0,0],"Properties":{"colgroup":"|","id":"20230723224548-ce9zncx","updated":"20230723224548"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Data":"thead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer 1         物理层 Physical Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"由于网络传输介质只能传输0与1 这种比特位，因此物理层必须定义所使用的传输设备的电压与信号等，同时还必须了解数据帧转成比特流的编码方式，最后连接实际传输介质并发送/接受比特信号"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer2                        数据链路层              Data-Link Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这一层是比较特殊的一层，因为其下层是实体的定义，而其上层则是软件封装的定义。因此第二层又分为两个子层进行数据的转换操作，在偏硬件介质部分，主要负责的是MAC(Madia Access Control) ,我们称这个数据包裹为MAC数据帧(frame),MAC 是网络接口设备所能处理的主要数据包裹，这也是最终被物理层编码成比特流的数据。MAC 必须要经过通信协议来取得网络介质的使用权。偏向软件的部分则是由逻辑链接层(Logical Link Control LLC) 所控制，主要在多任务处理来自上层的数据包数据 packet 并转成MAC 的格式，负责的工作包括信息交换，流量控制，失误问题的处理等。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer 3   网络层    etwork Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这一层定义IP ，也定义出计算机之间的连接建立、终止与维持等，数据数据包的传输路径选择等，这个层次当中最重要的除了IP之外，就是数据包能否到达目地的路由 route 概念"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer 4   传输层   Transport Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这一层定义了发送端与接收端的连接技术 如 TCO UDP 技术，同时包括该技术的数据包格式，数据包的发送，流程的控制、传输过程的侦测检查与重新传送等，以确保各个资料数据包可以正确无误的到达目的端"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer 5    会话层     Session Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"在这个层次当中主要定义了两个地址之间的连接信道的连接与中断，此外，也可建立应用程序之间的会话，提供其他加强型服务，如网络管理、建立与断开，会话控制等，如果说传输层是在判断数据包是否可以正确的到达目标，那么会话层则是在确定网络服务建立连接的确认，"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer6   表示层    Presentation Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我们通过应用程序生成出来的数据格式不一定符合网络传输的标准编码格式，所以在这个层次当中，最主要的操作就是将来自本地端应用程序的数据格式转换(或者是重新编码）成为网络的标准格式然后再交给下面的传输层等协议来进行处理，所以，在这个层次上面，主要定义的是网络服务（或程序）之间的数据格式的转换，包括数据的解密也是在这个层次上处理"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Layer 7 应用层  Application Layer"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"应用层本身并不属于应用程序所有，而是在定义应用程序如何进入该层的沟通接口，以将数据接收或发送给应用程序，并最终展给用户。"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td"},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td"}]}]},{"ID":"20230723224622-yn6yrty","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230723224622-yn6yrty"}}]}